# Lychee link-check ignore patterns for NovaTrek Architecture Platform
#
# Format: one pattern per line.
# Regex patterns are supported (see lychee docs).
# Lines starting with # are comments.

# ---- Azure Static Web Apps preview URLs ----
# These are ephemeral staging URLs generated per PR and are not persistent.
https://.*\.azurestaticapps\.net

# ---- Localhost / development URLs ----
# Referenced in implementation guides; not resolvable from CI.
http://localhost
http://127\.0\.0\.1

# ---- Internal Vikunja ticketing instance ----
# Self-hosted; not reachable from GitHub Actions runners.
https://vikunja\.

# ---- Azure portal and management endpoints ----
# Login-gated; will always return 401/403 in automated checks.
https://portal\.azure\.com
https://management\.azure\.com

# ---- GitHub Actions workflow run URLs ----
# Workflow run URLs are ephemeral and only valid when logged in.
https://github\.com/.*/actions/runs/

# ---- GitHub Actions workflow definition links ----
# These reference workflows that exist but require authentication to view.
https://github\.com/.*/actions/workflows/

# ---- Confluence instance ----
# Login-gated Atlassian Cloud; returns 401 for anonymous requests.
https://.*\.atlassian\.net

# ---- PlantUML server ----
# Referenced in documentation; may be rate-limited in CI.
https://plantuml\.com

# ---- NPM and package registries ----
# Sometimes flaky under CI network constraints.
https://www\.npmjs\.com
https://registry\.npmjs\.org
